\v 2 Ohlakaniphileyo angaphendula yini ulwazi olungumoya\x + 12.3. 13.2.\x*, agcwalise isisu sakhe\x + 15.35.\x* ngomoya wempumalanga\x + Hos. 12.1.\x*?
\v 3 Aphikise ngamazwi angasizi lutho\x + 22.2.\x*, langenkulumo ezingelanzuzo yini\x + 35.3.\x*?
\v 4 Yebo, wena uyachitha ukwesaba\x + 4.6.\x*, uvimbela umkhuleko phambi kukaNkulunkulu.
\v 5 Ngoba umlomo wakho ufundisa ububi bakho, ukhethe ulimi lwamaqili.
\v 6 Umlomo wakho uyakulahla, kayisimi\x + 9.20. Luka 19.22.\x*; yebo, indebe zakho ziyafakaza ngawe\x + 2 Sam. 1.16.\x*.
