\v 7 Ungumuntu wokuqala owazalwayo yini? Kumbe wazalwa mandulo\x + 26.5,13. Zaga 8.25. 25.23.\x* kwamaqaqa yini\x + Hlab. 90.2.\x*?
\v 8 Uzwile yini icebo langasese likaNkulunkulu\x + 29.4. Jer. 23.18. Roma 11.34.\x*? Kumbe uzigodlele inhlakanipho yini\x + 15.4.\x*?
\v 9 Kuyini okwaziyo esingakwaziyo? \add Kuyini\add* okuqedisisayo okungekho kithi\x + 13.2.\x*?
\v 10 Kukhona phakathi kwethu lempunga\x + 12.12. 32.6,7.\x* lekhehla, omdala ngensuku kuloyihlo\x + 2 Lan. 36.17.\x*.
\v 11 Zincinyane yini kuwe induduzo zikaNkulunkulu, lelizwi elikhulunywa kuhle lawe?
\v 12 Kungani inhliziyo yakho ikumukisa? Njalo kungani amehlo akho ephayiza,
\v 13 ukuthi uphendule umoya wakho umelane loNkulunkulu, ukhuphe amazwi \add anje\add* emlonyeni wakho\x + 21.4. Hlu. 8.3. Tshu. 7.9.\x*?
