\v 14 Umuntu uyini ukuthi abe ngohlambulukileyo\x + 15.16. 14.4. 25.4-6. 1 Kho. 8.46. 2 Lan. 6.36. Hlab. 14.3.\x*, lozelwe ngowesifazana ukuthi abe ngolungileyo\x + 14.1.\x*?
\v 15 Khangela, kathembeli\x + 4.18.\x* kwabangcwele bakhe\x + 5.1.\x*, lamazulu kawahlambulukanga emehlweni akhe.
\v 16 Kukangakanani umuntu onengekayo\x + 9.14. 4.19.\x* lowonakeleyo\x + Hlab. 14.3. 53.3.\x*, onatha ububi njengamanzi\x + 34.7. Hlab. 73.10. Zaga 26.6.\x*!
