\v 17 Ngizakutshengisa, ungilalele, lengikubonileyo ngizakulandisa,
\v 18 lokho izihlakaniphi\x + Isa. 3.9.\x* ezikukhulumileyo kusukela kuboyise\x + 8.8.\x*, njalo kazikufihlanga\x + Isa. 3.9.\x*,
\v 19 okwanikwa kuzo zodwa ilizwe, lokungadlulanga izihambi phakathi kwazo\x + Jow. 3.17.\x*.
\v 20 Insuku zonke zokhohlakeleyo uzizwisa ubuhlungu, lenani leminyaka ebekelelwe\x + 21.19. 24.1.\x* umcindezeli\x + 6.23.\x*.
\v 21 Umsindo wezethuso usendlebeni zakhe; empumelelweni umchithi uzamfikela\x + 1 Thes. 5.3.\x*.
\v 22 Kakholwa ukuthi uzaphenduka emnyameni, kodwa ukuthi ulindelwe yinkemba.
\v 23 Uzulela ukudla\x + Hlab. 59.15. 109.10.\x*. Kungaphi\x + 8.18. Eks. 18.4.\x*? Uyazi ukuthi usuku lobumnyama lulungisiwe esandleni sakhe\x + 18.12.\x*.
\v 24 Uhlupho losizi kuyamethusa, kumehlule\x + 14.20.\x* njengenkosi elungele impi\x + 29.25.\x*.
\v 25 Ngoba welule isandla sakhe emelene loNkulunkulu, wenza ngamandla ukumelana loSomandla.
