\v 28 Uhlala emizini echithekileyo, izindlu abangahlali kuzo, ezilungele ukuba zinqumbi.
\v 29 Kayikunotha, lenotho yakhe kayiyikuma, lenzuzo yakhe kayiyikusabalala emhlabeni.
\v 30 Kayikusuka emnyameni; ilangabi lizakomisa ihlumela lakhe\x + 8.16.\x*, njalo uzasuka ngokuphefumula komoya wakhe\x + 4.9. Isa. 33.11.\x*.
